{"tid":458607,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉江華：香港人尊重國家屬應有之義","createTime":"2017-11-05T05:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T07:01:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"10f609a8a75e479b17c234a729171fdae085b7ec","tid":458607,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509855756_c185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509855756_c185.jpg&h=6b11c721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大常委會昨通過將《國歌法》納入《基本法》附件三，港府將以本地立法方式，在港落實《國歌法》，港區人大葉國謙表明，將來市民聽到國歌必須肅立，甚至「行緊路都要停」，否則就會觸犯《國歌法》。民政事務局局長劉江華指，市民尊重國歌、國家和民族，屬應有之義。<br />\n<br />\n劉江華又指，港府已清楚表明，《國歌法》在本地立法時會諮詢公眾，完成整個立法程序後，相關部門如康文署等，會根據條文執法，詳細情況要視乎各部門配合。他又說，除立法外，亦要在教育層面推廣，過去公民教育委員會不遺餘力，增加市民對國歌的認識，例如電視新聞前會播放國歌，未來亦會加強宣傳。"},{"pid":"10764a7bf164802224879435ea8fb818a7a19b5a","tid":458607,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171105/57420049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171105%2F57420049&d=AVe2VvwzaJ11tKqN4%2Bn9uEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=07d721c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171105%2F57420049&h=79522472\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171105/57420049</a>"},{"pid":"1fc2051825dfd9aef780711599557f35e4388a4c","tid":458607,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:10:04.000Z","msg":"「國家」尊重香港人是痴心妄想"},{"pid":"9fbac98343bed1922167a062af331289ed6e9b2b","tid":458607,"uid":47480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:17:58.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 垃圾桶"},{"pid":"8f3611dd491d070260e0146545a882c39